Package eu.df.jiffybox.models

Class Disk

java.lang.Object
eu.df.jiffybox.models.Disk
public class Disk
extends java.lang.Object
A disk consists of a name, a filesystem, a size (in MB), a creation timestamp, a status and a distribution.
